  <summary>A markdown recipes application</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Do some cooking with some easy recipes. All the recipes are written in simple markdown. Don't see what you like? Add your own!</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
     <ul>
       <li>Read awesome recipes</li>
       <li>Easily add your own recipe by doing a PR.</li>
       <li>Multilangual</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
